Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:09.60,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}翻譯：提燈娃娃；後期：zipwinmax。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.26,0:00:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我高中二年級那年夏天的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全國麻將大賽縣預選已經結束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.74,0:00:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們風越女子中止了在團體戰連續多年進軍全國的腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那之後不久的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐  福路學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  怎麼了  池田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.27,0:00:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐  不是約好了要叫我名字的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊…怎麼了  華菜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.11,0:00:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…想找您商量些事…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的社團活動  可以允許我早退嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.12,0:00:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我會轉達給隊長的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:00:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪裡不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我沒生病…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是…今天是妹妹的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  妹妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.91,0:01:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且剛好今天爸爸媽媽很晚才會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.74,0:01:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去托兒所接她們回來然後做晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.24,0:01:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再見了  福路學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.59,0:01:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華菜怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是值得慶賀的事情  卻總是歎氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福路學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.28,0:01:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  吉留同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  您剛剛是在跟池田同學說話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  說是要去為妹妹慶祝生日  今天的社團活動請假呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:02:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…那樣還好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你在擔心什麼嗎  吉留同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她自從縣預選之後一直都沒什麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縣預選決賽輸給天江衣  果然一直都在自責嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  吉留同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.57,0:02:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道華菜的住址嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…明明應該是這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然經常一起放學  直接來到華菜家還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  打擾了…啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:03:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  是大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.63,0:03:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三胞胎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.76,0:03:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學…學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華菜  我來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…為什麼您會來？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我也想來給妹妹們慶生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶生！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫忙做飯的話  會給你添麻煩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪…哪裡的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好厲害的手藝啊  學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  華菜和小緋菜小菜沙小城菜都要吃飽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是謝謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華菜  不要總是自己一個人負擔著  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡事都追求完美的話會很累的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能幫上忙的話  隨時都可以來找我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐…真是多管閒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安  華菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要尿尿！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝太多果汁啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  下一個  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:19.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尿出來啦
